            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <a class="left carousel-control" href="http://getbootstrap.com/examples/carousel/#myCarousel" data-slide="prev"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left"></span></a>
    <a class="right carousel-control" href="http://getbootstrap.com/examples/carousel/#myCarousel" data-slide="next"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right"></span></a>
</div><!-- /.carousel -->
<div id="index">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm-12">

            <div class="cycle-slideshow" 
                data-cycle-fx="fade" data-cycle-slides="> div" data-cycle-timeout="5000">
                <div class="panel panel-info">
                    <div class="panel-heading">What is Autobot?</div>
                    <div class="panel-body">
                        ABL uses crowdfunding to provide a vehicle for their clients to increase earnings by:
				        Pooling small financial resources into large funds used to purchase equipment for lease by operator companies.  
                        It is expected that such equipment is used directly in their revenue producing processes.
				        Provide operators (lessees) with high quality equipment under flexible and reasonable lease terms.
				        Maintain visibility for ABL clients with regard to status of equipment they have purchased and leased 
                        out (e.g., production data, location, maintenance record, etc.).
				        Distribute profit shares produced by leased equipment back to participating ABL clients.
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="panel panel-info">
                    <div class="panel-heading">Why Join?</div>
                    <div class="panel-body">
                        ABL uses crowdfunding to provide a vehicle for their clients to increase earnings by:
